\s NI MPWEMU YAREMYE
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Ni Mpwemu yaremye vyose, ni Mpwemu wo hambere ni we twanyoyeko ku buntu, nkuko vyari vyasezeranywe.\bd*
\pc \bdit Ni Mpwemu w’\bdit*\bdit I\bdit*\bdit sezerano, aza kw’\bdit*\bdit I\bdit*\bdit jambo ry’\bdit*\bdit I\bdit*\bdit sezerano\bdit*\bdit  \bdit*\bdit ./.Riri mu bana b’\bdit*\bdit I\bdit*\bdit sezerano niwe Bugingo \bdit*\bdit Budashira\bdit*\bdit ./.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Ni Mpwemu w’Imana Data, tunywako umutaga n’ijoro, eka ntawomuhanga namba, n’Imana ubwayo muri twebwe.\bd*
\pc \bdit Ni Mpwemu w’Isezerano, aza kw’Ijambo ry’Isezerano ./.Riri mu bana b’Isezerano niwe Bugingo Budashira./.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Ni we ba Data bahaweko, yabarongora amanwa n’ijoro, uwo niwe Mpwemu twahawe, natwe niwe aturongora.\bd*
\pc \bdit Ni Mpwemu w’Isezerano, aza kw’Ijambo ry’Isezerano ./.Riri mu bana b’Isezerano niwe Bugingo Budashira./.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Uwumushaka wese naze, uwumunyotewe naze anywe, ari mw’ijambo ry’isezerano, niwo muco w’igihe cacu.\bd*
\pc \bdit Ni Mpwemu w’Isezerano, aza kw’Ijambo ry’Isezerano ./.Riri mu bana b’Isezerano niwe Bugingo Budashira./.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Yemwe ngenzi ni tureme, dufise umugabisha akomeye, atujana ahasezeranywe, ni Mpwemu Yera w’Imana.\bd*
\pc \bdit Ni Mpwemu w’Isezerano, aza kw’Ijambo ry’Isezerano ./.Riri mu bana b’Isezerano niwe Bugingo Budashira./.\bdit*
